\nChina took Chemical Bunker from GLA
\nWe need to retake it back."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG3
"Qattinah Lake
\nChina's Military AirBase."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG4
"GLA Leader made a secret deal with Gen.Shepherd
\nYou have to transport Toxin Supply
\nto Gen.Shepherd across of the Lake."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG5
"Mission Objective: #1
\nRegroup With GLA Armsdealer on the North
\nYou need more strength to aginst Chinese."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG6
"Incoming Transmission:
\nExcelent Brother 
\nNow Build Your forces and do Objective #2"
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG7
