\nCapture 5 Anthrax Bunker.
\nBeware about China's MIGs."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG8
"Incoming Transmission:
\nGen.Shepherd allow You to owns Oil Derricks.
\nMake as Strong Brother."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG9
"Bonus Objective:
\nCivilians in this town hate China's forces.
\nFree the market and let these people fight with us."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG10
"Brother, Dr.Thrax give you Chemical Rebel
