\nBeware The MIGs."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG12
"Mission Objective: #2
\nCapture 6 of Anthrax Bunker
\nand protect them at all costs."
END

MSNSTR:SUPZH:GLA:02:CAPTION_DIALOG13
